{"tid":868083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時開始做兄弟姊妹要比人情","createTime":"2018-10-19T07:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T08:50:18.000Z","uid":54973,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1cae821d4f725b7a0cf031f9b596a4171c3fe2c6","tid":868083,"uid":54973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"今日同同事傾計講開做兄弟比左幾多人情，老細（40幾歲）走過黎話做兄弟邊洗比人情架，佢以前結婚都唔會要兄弟做人情。<br />\n<br />\n到底幾時開始做兄弟要比人情？"},{"pid":"f9c7bd95997c00a0135071cf137bc09fbc6a6663","tid":868083,"uid":88743,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:59:15.000Z","msg":"新朗窮個時"},{"pid":"ea4531cf0d12768759ff68065924bf05f8ff9448","tid":868083,"uid":129810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"來幫手做牛做馬仲要俾人情？<br />\n唔問你攞番都偷笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbe09f3321a1152af14262afc1a1f9d162ab1cd","tid":868083,"uid":54973,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"但而家好似公認左兄弟姊妹一定要做人情咁。除非特別講明唔洗，唔係都預左你會比<br />\n<br />\n姊妹都話有開門利是可以幫補下，做兄弟做牛做馬仲要貼錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c62d859d7cc37a86ef8e5b61478cc4fe795eff","tid":868083,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"都係傾遮，主人家知道兄弟做人情，咁封幫手利是咪大封d"},{"pid":"eda8c4e08510dbbd297d769de68240641dbe61a2","tid":868083,"uid":39326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bbe09f3321a1152af14262afc1a1f9d162ab1cd","tid":868083,"uid":54973,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"但而家好似公認左兄弟姊妹一定要做人情咁。除非特別講明唔洗，唔係都預左你會比<br />\n<br />\n姊妹都話有開門利是可以幫補下，做兄弟做牛做馬仲要貼錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"乜唔係兄弟利是比幾多, 人情做返幾多咩, 兩次都係朝早收到600. 夜晚入返比人"},{"pid":"7c414217244298508141e4a79de69ada242f402b","tid":868083,"uid":9670,"like":1,"d